Value Required neighbor_hostname (.*)
Value Required local_interface (\S+)
Value Required neighbor_interface (.*)
Value neighbor_ip (\d+?\.\d+?\.\d+?\.\d+?|\w+?\.\w+?\.\w+?)
Value system_description (.*)


Start
  ^Remote LLDP.+Port ${local_interface}:
  ^\s+Chassis.+, Port ${neighbor_interface}:
  ^\s+System Name\s+\=\s${neighbor_hostname},
  ^\s+System\sDescription\s+\=\s${system_description}$$
  ^\s+Management IP Address\s+\=\s${neighbor_ip}, -> Record